{"tid":2414584,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（單車撚）住天水圍北嘅麻煩你入一入黎。","createTime":"2021-02-19T13:36:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T03:22:57.000Z","uid":195933,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f03f7855140bdcb2d54def691f153bf22898c81c","tid":2414584,"uid":195933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:36:14.000Z","msg":"是咁的。小弟住天水圍北，日前買咗一架單車代步，平日返工踩單車經臭河來回天水圍西鐵站。咁當中就會途經天秀到天澤商場嘅單車徑。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而果條近天澤商場嘅單車徑入口係收工時段（1800-1900）左右，都會有好多人聚集，通常都有一班中年麻甩佬係度食煙飲酒吹水，有時會係阿婆擺地攤賣菜。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁入口個位本身已經係窄，再成日企咁多人係度真係好危險。何況佢地仲係單車徑食煙。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nUxSXTj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnUxSXTj.jpg&h=0111cc89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢張係天澤商場方向影過去。今日（2月19號）早上0730左右，又有阿婆賣野，屌。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁不嬲都係咁踩我都無特別理佢地。琴日下午六點半左右，我離遠望到個單車徑入口塞住咗，有一中年漢坐係單車度，停低咗同班男人吹水，咁右邊單車徑出口仲有足夠嘅位過，我就叮咗幾下再入去爬佢頭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5P2ccEn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5P2ccEn.jpg&h=29d1ba60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紅色箭嘴係入口，藍色係出口。<br />\n<br />\n咁一直踩到果條單車徑嘅盡頭，到咗果個少少斜位同分岔口。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BfZh8Wb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBfZh8Wb.jpg&h=98fd0ea2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n藍色箭咀係我行嘅路線。當時紅色交叉位有一個行人。<br />\n<br />\n本身呢個位又多人，又暗斜，所以我見側邊有路人行梗我咪落車（同埋單車徑其實已經完咗，理應落車）。<br />\n<br />\n然後後面個踩梗單車嘅男人就屌我老母，我咪另轉頭問佢：&ldquo;你講咩話？&rdquo;我諗果個男人好有可能係剛才塞住單車徑入口果位。佢答：&ldquo;屌你呀&rdquo; 我承認我一時上火：&ldquo;屌你老母做乜撚野，落車吖！撞撚死你呀！&rdquo;咁佢繼續屌，我就慢慢推我架車，到我慢慢行到入俊宏軒個路口，見佢落咗車，拎起條單車鎖鏈眼有兇光咁望住我幾秒，我就無出聲望返佢，佢見我無乜動作就繼續行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hTK2ABk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhTK2ABk.jpg&h=1e6362f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖中紅色交叉係廢老企個位，藍色交叉係我企個位。<br />\n<br />\n我想講返嘅係，雖然我並無因個男人行為驚到瀨尿掉頭走，但我多少覺得我嘅人生安全被侵犯。我只係係行人路上停止踩單車，結果就俾惡人鬧同兇，而果班廢老就繼續日日收工時間覇住單車徑，又係非吸煙區煲煙，亦無視限聚令，實在令人髮指。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TbFECPf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTbFECPf.jpg&h=6cac6c1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k7FQKud.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk7FQKud.jpg&h=02f02f13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n琴日我同咗當區區議員王伯羽講，佢叫我報1823+食環。今日我決定報狗+控煙辦+報食環，等你班撚樣搞鳩我。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hT0twex.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhT0twex.jpg&h=040fbf7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cgh7MJm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgh7MJm.jpg&h=5fff4e7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4ZCvKu3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4ZCvKu3.jpg&h=5257fdc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以上為今日下午六點半偷拍，差唔多七點時有成十個人不過我無影到。<br />\n<br />\n你班廢老仲唔冚家產。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n強烈呼籲住天水圍嘅大家一起舉報呢班仆街。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecc07dac759fe6db7bd3404f66b25d3ef69aa950","tid":2414584,"uid":195933,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:37:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XotF6OC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXotF6OC.jpg&h=b20afc98&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c75b91fac890b5246e8f376673a43900eaf2a4f9","tid":2414584,"uid":195933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:39:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"341d240f1f65bd903fe90193cbf440a12612a5bf","tid":2414584,"uid":195933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:40:14.000Z","msg":"以後見一次就報一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26f6f0f8401f4f182d71d9ccbbca0a3dacb1664e","tid":2414584,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:41:32.000Z","msg":"惺咁渣ga"},{"pid":"79d34cac9181de541f6b59a70f854561b6e2bcba","tid":2414584,"uid":354403,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:41:49.000Z","msg":"我覺得1823有用啲"},{"pid":"0174847428dce52e513170c7a83cb6b862f20efa","tid":2414584,"uid":195933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"79d34cac9181de541f6b59a70f854561b6e2bcba","tid":2414584,"uid":354403,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:41:49.000Z","msg":"我覺得1823有用啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:43:43.000Z","msg":"今日打去錄音留言咗了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d3df5f021c43de2557fff78ef9bf7b984c32841","tid":2414584,"uid":243380,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:44:40.000Z","msg":"咁多位係要揀果度聚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fcc8ac4f9e37a36c30f203cbd5a3a61e266767b","tid":2414584,"uid":195933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"26f6f0f8401f4f182d71d9ccbbca0a3dacb1664e","tid":2414584,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:41:32.000Z","msg":"惺咁渣ga"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:45:09.000Z","msg":"sorry <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我無驚 但無醒起其實我有條更粗更大的銷車鏈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"810c148bd85063d92689919bd0bd55d0ec0a60f8","tid":2414584,"uid":195933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score